      <description>&lt;p&gt;Invited single-day hackathon project with Antonia Manhatsberger, for the production of an interactive audiovisual installation for the &lt;em&gt;Sonic Rug&lt;/em&gt;, developed by Selina Reiterer and Oliver Maklott.&lt;/p&gt;
&lt;p&gt;&amp;ldquo;Sonic Rug is the result of an artistic approach to smart textiles.Â The project is exploring the possibilities of connecting soft material to the digital space, manifesting the results within an interactive installation, that creates sounds by touch. [&amp;hellip;] In this Hackathon data from the touch-sensitive installation will be open to be translated into different media.&amp;rdquo;&lt;sup id=&#34;fnref:1&#34;&gt;&lt;a href=&#34;#fn:1&#34; class=&#34;footnote-ref&#34; role=&#34;doc-noteref&#34;&gt;1&lt;/a&gt;&lt;/sup&gt;&lt;/p&gt;

